author: @potato-sweet
text: For those who have a mac, I managed to figure out how to get MySQL! I had to watch a separate video to explain it, but in short, you'll need to download the installer (community server) and the workbench separately. If you go on the My SQL website, go to downloads, and then scroll down to MySQL Community (GPL) Downloads, you'll find the option for getting the community server and workbench separately. There are a few other steps involved so I recommend watching a different video dedicated to getting it on a Mac  My last comment got deleted, so instead of adding the link, the name of the video that helped me was 'How to Install MySQL on Mac' by ProgrammingKnowledge. Hope that helps!
